title: Coast to Coast AM - 05-14-10 - Rendlesham Forest Incident
description:
Date:
 05-14-10
 
Host:
 George Noory
 
Guests:
 James Fox 
 


During the first half of the program, documentary filmmaker James Fox, along with witnesses James Penniston and Paul Tuzinski, discussed the Rendlesham Forest/Bentwaters AFB UFO incident. 

Open Lines followed. The final half hour featured a replay of George's 6/13/08 interview with writer Marc Zicree and Anne Serling, daughter of The Twilight Zone creator Rod Serling.
